text: LeeLee Morrison-Henry (born 2 October 1960) is a Canadian freestyle skier. She was born in Norwood, Massachusetts, United States. She competed at the 1992 Winter Olympics, in women's moguls. == References == == External links == * Category:1960 births Category:People from Norwood, Massachusetts Category:Living people Category:Canadian female freestyle skiers Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Canada Category:Freestyle skiers at the 1992 Winter Olympics
